title: Move into our renovated 1 bedroom apartment and receive up to $1500!
neighborhood: 6624 West Broadway Avenue, Brooklyn Park, MN
posting_body: ['West Broadway Apartments has a renovated 1 bedroom apartment available now.', 'Our current move-in special is $100 off market rent with a 12-month lease and $300 off move-in costs.', 'Living in this beautiful apartment community provides great amenities to keep you busy.', 'Shoot some hoops on our community basketball court, entertain friends outside in our picnic area, and more!', 'West Broadway Apartments is all about providing you with the most comfortable and convenient lifestyle.', 'We are a short commute from restaurants, businesses, and plenty of parks to get outside and enjoy the beauty of nature!', 'Our apartments provide easy access to Interstate 94 and Highway 169, making commuting to work or running errands a breeze!', "We are also conveniently located just 10 minutes from N Lyndale Ave, our city's bustling downtown area.", 'Find out why our residents love living at West Broadway Apartments!', 'Schedule a tour today.', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Pet Friendly', '-Cable Ready', '-Air Conditioner', '-Picnic Area', '-Off', 'Street Parking', '-Online Payment Options', '-Basketball Court', '-Garages Available', '-Public Transportation', '-Refrigerator', '-Carpeting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 9AM-5PM', '6624 West Broadway Avenue, Brooklyn Park, MN, USA, Brooklyn Park, MN 55428', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
